Grodbog grubs can be found at Brúvraum in western Máttugard.\n\nYou should stomp the grodbog grubs.

The passage of Brúvraum has become a vile insect hive where gredbyg have claimed this area in Máttugard. Amongst the hives, many small grodbog grubs squirm and move about. If this grodbog hive is to ever cease in growing, these grubs will have to be destroyed.
